why do people write -1 after something like FindAbilityByName("ability"):GetLevel() - 1 ?
Shush 20-Mar-18 04:49 AM
because lua is 1 indexed while dota runs in C++ which is 0 indexed
i.e. if you start an array then the first element in lua is 1 while in C++ it's 0
so the first level in lua is 1, first level in C++ is 0
so you do -1 to match
